    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you <strong>already</strong> have test classes you may:</p>\n\n<p>1) Put a cursor on a class declaration and press <code>Alt</code> + <code>Enter</code>. In the dialogue choose JUnit and press <code>Fix</code>. This is a standard way to create test classes in IntelliJ.</p>\n\n<p>2) Alternatively you may add JUnit jars manually (download from site or take from IntelliJ files).</p>\n"
