    "answer_id" : 64433728,
    "question_id" : 4757800,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case (IntelliJ 2020-02, Kotlin dev) JUnit library was already included by Create project wizard. I needed to enable JUnit plugin:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/r1UzP.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/r1UzP.png\" alt=\"IntelliJ JUnit plugin\" /></a></p>\n<p>to get green Run test icons next to each test class and method:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5GQo9.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5GQo9.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>and CTRL+Shift+R will run test under caret, and CTRL+shift+D to debug.</p>\n"
  } ],
