  "title" : "Configuring IntelliJ IDEA for unit testing with JUnit",
  "body" : "<p>I decided to try out IntelliJ this morning via the trial version and installed the JUnit plugin. I made a new Java project and I want to write a test case for it.</p>\n\n<p>How do I add the junit.jar file to my project? (I actually want to add it to every java project, now and forever more - is there a way of doing that?).</p>\n"
